### Get my reports
GET {{baseUrl}}/reports?page=1&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get report by id
GET {{baseUrl}}/reports/6a2574e7295614e33642a2b1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Update report metadata
PUT {{baseUrl}}/reports/6a257eb8295614e33642a2b4
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Updated sales analysis",
  "tags": ["sales", "updated"],
  "descriptionCategory": "sales"
}

### Soft delete report
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/reports/6a257eb8295614e33642a2b4
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}